    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The college offered courses through flexi learn system which helps students select the courses they are interested in completing for the academic year.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "i liked the most in my college is like conducting event days and also taking to industrial visits and providing good knowledge about industries",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college is spacious containing vast number of cafetirias, grounds and many club activities.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "the infrastructure of the college is good and also high end computers are provided to us and mainly new courses are introduced in every semester",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Infrastructure are really amazing  labs are good",
          "name": "Kavi",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "I like my collage  infastructure and the facilities provided. tyhey have kind and good faculties who help in all the domains. we can freely talk to the faculties amd well mentored. they help in providing a good education and wisely treated. good good",
          "name": "MAHALAKSHMI U",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Taste , quality of food is very nice and delicious.",
          "name": "T BHUPAL",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "First of all the freedom in this college was too good ,here theres no strict rules like other engineering colleges ,it's like in our hands we should be obedient,and maintain our integrity and enjoy our college life",
          "name": "Abdullah R",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The hostel Life:it's the best hostel compared to others for each meal time there has been min 2-3 menus and the foods are too good,and ac's in rooms are top notch",
          "name": "Abdullah R",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The infrastructure of the college very improved and digitalized class rooms",
          "name": "GIFTSON RAJARATHINAM N",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "There are some facilities that needs proper maintainance like WI-FI and proper drinking water facilities.",
          "name": "Review Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "i mostly disappointed on the exam system like we should write in our free time slots and also the slots booking will be done in seconds and cannot get the desired time slots",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "i'am  not  satisfied  with  the  placements  on  \"ECE dept\" . and compared to other dept. . as iam from ece dept.  they say they provided   \"0 pracements\"  on the previous year  which  make  us  derpressed  and  brings  more  fear  .they  have    to",
          "name": "MAHALAKSHMI U",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "they   have  to improve  the  system  in  which  we are  not  able  to learn  the fullest  about  the subject  and we  are  not able  to know  about  the  concepts  . they  have  to know  about  the time  management  on teaching  the subjects  . ....",
          "name": "MAHALAKSHMI U",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "From my point of view ,the fees structure is too heavy apart from that I don't have any dislikes",
          "name": "Abdullah R",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "They don't allow students to come college by bike if anyone come in bike into campus they'll seize the bike and fine them",
          "name": "GIFTSON RAJARATHINAM N",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "There will be no enough time for the cia completion they will close it within 10days",
          "name": "GIFTSON RAJARATHINAM N",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "We don't have books to study and everything is laptop and mobiles so we just need to search and explore that on our own",
